{"type": "article", "id": 54022, "title": "一套注重各部位平衡关系的刀具，用起来很轻盈｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-06T23:21:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50912, "name": "Koncept"}, {"id": 17302, "name": "Layer"}, {"id": 50913, "name": "Todot Design"}, {"id": 50914, "name": "挑时Tells"}, {"id": 50915, "name": "NormannCopenhagen"}, {"id": 50916, "name": "Di Lu"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180606214135mfvtOyxoDBGi9TaL.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Mesh Chef's Knife Steel by NormannCopenhagen</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 NormannCopenhagen 推出易于操作又造型精美的刀具系列 Mesh，出自设计师 Simon Legald 之手。Mesh 在刀柄上做足文章，不同于通常光滑的表面，Mesh<i> </i>的刀柄以精细的网格状印花作为装饰，看上去好似手掌的纹路。这些纹路增加了手掌与刀具之间的摩擦，使 Mesh 在使用时更加舒适且不易从手中滑落。同时，设计师注重刀具各部位的平衡关系， 从刀尖到刀柄做到重量的合适分布。这样一来，使 Mesh 在手感上更加轻盈，用起来也更加轻松。</p><p>整个系列刀具以手工焊接的不锈钢制成，包含 5 把不同功用的刀具: 面包刀，厨师刀，蔬菜刀，全功能刀和削皮刀。售价 75 美元，<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/en/Products/Accessories/Kitchen-Utensils/Mesh-Chefs-Knife-Metallic-330536\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214303XD42boc5PQeGnKMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214303krI8pQ0Ht41A7jBn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214303mQoOyNRaVw84kSKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214303OTSWB1XlpxdIntfE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214304WqEgcAGTpkyhm7dZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Talking 汉堡小沙发 by 挑时Tells</h3><p>设计品牌挑时Tells 推出 Talking 汉堡小沙发，一大一小凑成一对儿，大人与孩子可以坐在属于自己的沙发上聊天，这也是 Talking 这个名字的来源。</p><p>在试用过程中，设计师发现朋友们来家里做客，都爱坐在这张 MINI 沙发上，迷你的尺寸让大人们围坐在一起距离更近，大伙儿还给它取了小名叫“汉堡”。软包的体量，金属的特有弧度，都增加了制作的难度。提供橘色、丝绒黑、丝绒粉以及丝绒绿 4 种配色，售价 1680 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-14948482991.59.760f31a44PVjBZ&amp;id=558314299896\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214334ckJteorLnY42T85Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214334gOR4fInwJX9FoWLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214335mFYIoqcX4HR1BftM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214334ux3vdy9gWkKsACzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.893333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214336Rd76C4YcKITwLhJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.726667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ultratime 002 Watch by Todot Design</h3><p>以“月球另一面的秘密”为概念，Todot Design 设计了 ULTRATIME 002 手表。手表被一分为二，黑色部分如同月球神秘的另一面，而另一半则用鲜活的色彩来演绎时间。</p><p>ULTRATIME 002 采用了全新的时间显示方式，将 12 个小时浓缩到 6 个刻度上，每个刻度同时代表两个时段，两个时段相隔 6 个小时。大点代表1个小时，小点代表10分钟，用半圆形的彩色转盘替代指针功能，右边色块的分割线就是当下的时间。售价 699 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c-s.w4002-16348305108.24.6345629buo8VEb&amp;id=560456888888\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214443bBDtxaUpGL4eSRo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806062144437fEIQXr5JyaDv8MN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214443k0bXUSP8yFRofLtg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214443aOcK3H6xuwnoFN8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214443HMUd1xQu7i3RKlza.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Trove by Layer</h3><p>由英国产品设计师 Benjamin Hubert 创立的 Layer 工作室，与金融科技初创公司 Trove 合作推出了一款名为 Trove 的数字钱包，可以帮助用户更安全、更便捷地存储和管理比特币等数字货币，不用担心丢失或被盗。</p><p>Trove 由四部分组成，包括 Coin，Keep，Safe 和Trove 智能手机应用程序，它的核心部件是 Coin，一种小型可穿戴设备，便于携带，也可以像配饰一样戴在身上，内置 ECG 传感器，需要用户与设备正面感应区接触几秒钟才能解锁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214645tjyVPiLvD71CexZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214649flBe9o3jRE5KIXLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.222504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214821Mj2scRgvQZC86mSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.917936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214830XxJmBczZSP6QjCTi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214832G56XCo9xf0c3OnPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214835zxFCaQ7sRYeMT5Jf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214835UvaJeiksWTA5uxfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.124788\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/06/05/layer-benjamin-hubert-trove-cryptocurrency-wallet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SHARPEN SMARTER by Di Lu</h3><p>如果你削过铅笔的话，可能会遇到笔屑、刨花飞散很难打理的状况，设计师 Di Lu 针对这种情况，设计了一款全新的卷笔刀，它有一个碗状铅笔屑出口，能盛装不少笔屑，用户可以一次性收集所有笔屑，然后将其一次性倒掉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214910WDMEm4SOwyuUk9RH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214911TfQysEGCHXZhpu4t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214912FNlCXBp7gdoDWkhf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.084762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214913yjUdxzqShPCf1RQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.075238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606214914Olw6cTEZ9I2UfRby.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mr N Lamp by Koncept</h3><p>Mr N 是美国照明公司 Koncept 推出的一款台灯，高约 190 毫米，厚度仅 7 毫米。灯具外形酷似英文小写字母 n，呈拱形，整个曲面都可以发散光线，灯具亮度可调范围为 1%至 100%，触摸控制，可用作阅读台灯、氛围灯或者小夜灯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606215002ab9NmwVqcJPIkRFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606215002dXUM1SgxpjKCWAht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.846250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606215003FNkwStOH2yxXBcZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180606215003LXzTbVsierw4qPID.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.458750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018060621500215QVJBdWtjXr0xPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.koncept.com/Mr-n\" rel=\"nofollow\">Koncept</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}